name:                buffer:
stack:               ( u -- )    compilation
                     ( -- a )    execution
return stack:        ( -- )
string stack:        ( -- )
contexts:            stateless
category:            definining word
input stream:        word

description:         create a word which returns the first address of u
                     reserved memory locations. Reserve those u memory locations

